		icon: {id: "botania:gaia_head", Count: 1b}
		description: ["You have completed the Magical Flora side chapter, defeating the Gaia Guardian II and mastering the Botania system from Livingwood through Elven trade and the Gaia gear tier. Botania's deep integration with the pack — Terrasteel gates, Mana-powered Enchanter, Elven materials — is behind you and available as ongoing production infrastructure. The Lexica Botania is now a reference, not a guide."]
