		icon: {id: "minecraft:nether_star", Count: 1b}
		description: ["You have completed every side chapter in the questbook — Magical Flora, Storage Solutions, Homestead, Professions, Power Generation, Applied Energistics 2, Mystical Agriculture, Quality of Life, Exploration, Fishing, and Other Hobbies. The pack did not ask you to do this. Most players never will. You chose to see the whole thing.", "The factory produces everything. The greenhouse generates everything. The ME network manages everything. The trains run on their own, the airship is fueled, the fishing farm runs in the background, and every dimension in the pack has a waystone in it. This is the full version of the playthrough. There is nothing left in the book you have not done."]
